title: Did the Rengar rework change anything?
body: I mean, I obviously just got blown up by a fed Rengar, and came here to QQ, but it doesn't seem like his change made him any less frustrating to play against. Please downvote me.

replies.body: Giving him free crit after his ult was just too dumb to begin with. Knew this would happen since I first saw the changes lol
